<Layout>
  <section class="smart-start-hero">
    <div class="smart-start-hero-content">
      <div class="smart-start-image-wrapper">
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Website%20Smart%20start%20header-o3O0F42PMslRXtuA00yX6sTZGZdpeL.jpg" alt="Multi-generational family" class="family-image" />
      </div>
      <div class="smart-start-branding">
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Logo_Smart%20Start%20-%20White%402x-XsgqCSJBhoO4brk80RcacqCWNvp7mx.png" alt="Smart Start" class="smart-start-logo" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="smart-start-description">
    <div class="description-container">
      <p class="description-text">
        Smart Start is TechNest's community program created to give back to the Chicagoland area we are proud to call home. Each month we choose one household or small business to receive a complimentary smart technology upgrade that makes everyday life a little easier, safer or more enjoyable. The program is built on genuine care, local impact and the belief that everyone deserves comfort, security and convenience. Anyone can enter or nominate a neighbor, and every Smart Start project highlights how thoughtful, well installed technology can create real change for real people in our community.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="how-it-works-container">
      <h2 class="how-it-works-title">HOW IT WORKS</h2>
      
      <div class="how-it-works-intro">
        <p>Smart Start is designed to be simple for everyone in the Chicagoland community. Each month, we select one household or small business to receive a complimentary smart technology upgrade that makes a real difference in their everyday life. Anyone can enter or nominate someone else, and the process is straightforward from start to finish.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-container">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Enter or nominate</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Complete a short form about yourself or someone you would like to nominate and explain how a smart upgrade would make everyday life easier.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Review and selection</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Every entry is carefully reviewed. Each month we select one household or small business where technology can genuinely improve comfort, safety or convenience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Plan the solution</h3>
          <p class="step-description">We speak with the selected recipient, assess their space and design the right smart solution. We take care of the products and planning.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Install and support</h3>
          <p class="step-description">Our team installs everything with care and makes sure it works properly, leaving the recipient confident and comfortable using it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h3 class="step-title">Share the impact</h3>
          <p class="step-description">With your permission, we share the story to show how thoughtful technology can make a real difference.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="cta-container">
      <div class="cta-image-wrapper">
        <img src="https://hebbkx1anhila5yf.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/Website%20Smart%20Start%20CTA%20section%20Lady-glIVbcp2zGFhhmGK3p1SFHAxQjADek.jpg" alt="Woman in craft studio" class="cta-image" />
      </div>
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Enter or Nominate an individual, couple, family or small business</h2>
        <a href="/smart-start-form" class="cta-button">Enter or Nominate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faqs-section">
    <div class="faqs-container">
      <div class="faqs-wrapper">
        <div class="faqs-column">
          <h3 class="faqs-title">FAQs</h3>
          <div class="faqs-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Who can apply or be nominated?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">Anyone living or operating a small business in the Chicagoland area can be entered. You do not need to be a TechNest customer.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Does the person I nominate need to know about it?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">No. You can nominate someone privately, and we will only contact them if they are selected.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Is Smart Start only for people in need?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">No. The program is open to everyone. Whether someone has moved into a new home, wants to improve comfort or security or could benefit from a more reliable setup, Smart Start is for the whole community.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">What type of upgrades are included?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">Upgrades may include smart security, lighting, networking, audio, smart automation or a combination of services that meaningfully improve daily life or business operations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">How often is someone selected?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">We select one household or small business every month.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Is there any cost to take part?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">No. If you are selected, the upgrade and installation are provided at no cost as part of our commitment to giving back to the community.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">What happens after someone is chosen?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">We contact the selected household or business, learn more about their needs and plan the upgrade. We handle all installation and setup.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Will my story or photos be shared publicly?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">We only share stories, photos or videos with your permission. You can still participate without agreeing to public sharing.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">How long does the process take?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">Most Smart Start upgrades are scheduled and completed within the month after selection.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
              <button class="faq-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
                <span class="faq-question">Can businesses participate?</span>
                <svg class="faq-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
              </button>
              <p class="faq-answer">Yes. Small businesses in the Chicagoland area are encouraged to enter or be nominated.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="eligibility-column">
          <h3 class="eligibility-title">ELIGIBILITY</h3>
          <ul class="eligibility-list">
            <li>Applicants or nominees must live or operate a small business within the Chicagoland area.</li>
            <li>Entries may be submitted by the individual themselves or by a friend, family member, neighbor or community member.</li>
            <li>You may only enter or nominate once per month.</li>
            <li>If selected, you can only be a recipient once and will not be eligible for future Smart Start selections.</li>
            <li>Only one household or business will be chosen each month.</li>
            <li>Selected recipients must be available for a short consultation and installation scheduling.</li>
            <li>Installations must take place in a location that the nominee owns, rents or lawfully operates.</li>
            <li>Upgrades will be chosen by the TechNest team based on the needs and suitability of the space.</li>
            <li>Recipients must be at least 18 years old or have a parent or guardian involved in the process.</li>
            <li>Participants are not required to be existing TechNest customers.</li>
            <li>Story or photo sharing is optional and not required for eligibility.</li>
            <li>TechNest reserves the right to make final selections based on safety, suitability and program capacity.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="second-cta-section">
    <div class="second-cta-container">
      <div class="second-cta-content">
        <h2 class="second-cta-title">Nominate to make<br/>someone's day or<br/>Enter to win!</h2>
        <a href="/smart-start-form" class="second-cta-button">Enter or Nominate</a>
      </div>
